WITH movie_aggregate AS (
    SELECT 
        mt.id AS movie_id,
        mt.title,
        mt.production_year,
        COUNT(DISTINCT ci.person_id) AS num_cast_members,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT ak.name, ', ') AS cast_names
    FROM 
        aka_title mt
    JOIN 
        complete_cast cc ON mt.id = cc.movie_id
    JOIN 
        cast_info ci ON cc.subject_id = ci.id
    JOIN 
        aka_name ak ON ci.person_id = ak.person_id
    WHERE 
        mt.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2023
    GROUP BY 
        mt.id, mt.title, mt.production_year
),

keyword_aggregate AS (
    SELECT 
        mk.movie_id,
        STRING_AGG(k.keyword, ', ') AS keywords
    FROM 
        movie_keyword mk
    JOIN 
        keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
    GROUP BY 
        mk.movie_id
)

SELECT 
    ma.title,
    ma.production_year,
    ma.num_cast_members,
    ma.cast_names,
    ka.keywords
FROM 
    movie_aggregate ma
LEFT JOIN 
    keyword_aggregate ka ON ma.movie_id = ka.movie_id
ORDER BY 
    ma.production_year DESC, 
    ma.title ASC

SELECT COALESCE("t7"."TITLE", "t7"."TITLE") AS "TITLE", "t7"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t7"."NUM_CAST_MEMBERS", "t7"."CAST_NAMES", "t7"."KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT "t5"."TITLE", "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t5"."NUM_CAST_MEMBERS", "t5"."CAST_NAMES", "t1"."KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", LISTAGG("keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM "keyword"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "keyword"."id" = "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
GROUP BY "movie_keyword"."movie_id") AS "t1"
RIGHT JOIN (SELECT MIN("t2"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t2"."title" AS "TITLE", "t2"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."person_id") AS "NUM_CAST_MEMBERS", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "CAST_NAMES"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "aka_title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000 AND "production_year" <= 2023) AS "t2"

INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id") ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "s1"."id"
GROUP BY "t2"."id", "t2"."title", "t2"."production_year") AS "t5" ON "t1"."MOVIE_ID" = "t5"."MOVIE_ID"
